Title: Playing Temporal HTML Documents  
Author: Franck Rousseau Andrzej Duda 
Address: 2, avenue de Vignate 38610 Gieres, France  BP 72 38402 St Martin d'Heres Cedex, France  
Affiliation: The Open Group Research Institute  LSR-IMAG  
Abstract: The WWW has become a major publishing medium. To integrate synchronized multimedia in this environment in a seamless way we propose temporal extensions to HTML and an execution architecture to support these extensions. We have created a prototype using Java and adapted it to make it run in a standard browser. 
